 a university student running a marathon in each of Australia 's eight states and territories to honour the memory of his late childhood friend .
Callum Ryan , 21 , committed himself to the challenge of running eight of them between January and September 2015 - covering a total distance of 337.5 kilometres .
His ` Eight Great States ' campaign is driven by his passion to make a difference after the loss of Malachy Frawley who died from heart disease in 2013 when he was 14 years old .